section:
    Grand Unified Custom Variables (GUCs)


This section lists custom PostGIS Grand Unified Custom Variables (GUC).
These can be set globally, by database, by session or by transaction. Best set at global or database level.

For more examples of usage refer to SQL SET 
    and SQL ALTER SYSTEM



